item.title: CVE-2015-9105|2024-08-06T08:36:31.894Z -- synology -- video%20station
item.description: Multiple cross-site scripting (XSS) vulnerabilities in Synology Video Station 1.2 before 1.2-0455, 1.5 before 1.5-0772, and 1.6 before 1.6-0847 allow remote authenticated attackers to inject arbitrary web script or HTML via the (1) file name or (2) collection name of videos.
